1. INTRODUCTION

Bouncy the spaceball has  got  himself  lost.  You  have  to guide him
through five different areas  back to  his  home.  Each  area features
five puzzling levels.  Some  are  very  simple,   others   are not. To
complete a level you must have  the  key  that  opens the exit. It may
sound easy but there are several obstacles in your path.

In this demo version there are  seven levels, taken from various areas
of the game.

