3. PLAYING BOUNCY

Bouncy is controlled by the joystick.

UP - JUMP UP

RIGHT - JUMP RIGHT

LEFT - JUMP LEFT

To restart any level press any mouse key.

Bouncy can  only  change  direction  or   jump   has  he  touches  the
platform, ie pushing the joystick  to  the  left will result in bouncy
jumping left once he touches the platform.

To jump onto a higher platform  you  must  push  the joystick up as he
bounces then push left or  right  when  he reaches the correct height.
Bouncy can fall  from  any  height  but  if  he  falls  off the bottom
platform he will die.

Bouncy will pick  up  any  object  he  contacts.  The  objects will be
displayed at the top of the screen.


